    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single below-threshold factor (Test conditions, achieved 1 vs. required 2) is offset by the strong quantitative output comparison results (all E/uval < 1.96) and cross-laboratory, cross-code agreement among three independent FEA implementations. The numerical simulation ensemble is judged to provide verification evidence of equivalent weight to a formal experimental-validation campaign, given the consistency of results. Overall credibility is sufficient to support the Medium model risk level and Medium decision consequence classification.",
